A city where all individualities work together

In this future, every technology is implemented in the right way, and the city is full of vitality as each one works together . There are fewer companies with bases, and people working in cities do not belong to a single company, but instead work while making use of their individuality and creating various collaborations . Yes, this is ``kaonavi Town'' , a town where all individualities work together , a form of the future several decades from now.
